sequenceDiagram
    participant F as Flutter客户端
    participant G as JwtGuard
    participant C as CourseController
    participant S as CourseService
    participant DB as SQLite数据库

    F->>G: POST /api/enrollments (Bearer Token)
    G->>G: 验证JWT令牌
    G->>C: 注入用户信息
    C->>S: createEnrollment(userId, courseId)
    S->>DB: 查询是否已报名
    DB-->>S: 无重复记录
    S->>DB: 插入Enrollment记录
    DB-->>S: 写入成功
    S-->>C: 返回报名结果
    C-->>F: 200 {enrollment}
